.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-RECEIVABLE-STDDEV" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-receivable-stddev \- FEAT-2831 channel-receivable-stddev
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-receivable-stddev
.SH DESCRIPTION
Computes the standard deviation of receivable_msat across all peer channels for the lightning CLI (FEAT-2831).
.PP
Output: JSON from CLN with key \fIreceivable_stddev_msat\fR.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning(1)
